    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert content strategist.\n\n**Goal:** Create a single, catchy line (max 8–10 words) from the given LinkedIn post text.  \nThis line should:\n- Capture the essence of the post.\n- Be visually impactful, as it will be used for an image or banner.\n- Avoid hashtags, emojis, or special characters.\n- Use simple, powerful words.\n- Remove any additional commentary. Only keep the post content and nothing else.\n\n**Input Post:** \n{{ $json.post }}\n\n**Output Format (JSON):**\n{\n  \"headline\": \"Your 1-line image headline here\"\n}",
        "batching": {}
      },
